---

<Layout title="About Us" description={SITE.DESCRIPTION}>
  <Container class="flex flex-col gap-y-6">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'About Us', icon: 'lucide:info' }]} />

    <section>
      <div class="min-w-full">
        <div class="prose prose-neutral mb-8 dark:prose-invert max-w-full">
          
          <h1>Day Agency</h1>
          <div class="lead">
            <p>
              Day Agency is a dynamic freelance agency based in Iran, offering a diverse range of professional services to businesses worldwide. Whether you need short-term support for a single project or long-term collaboration, our skilled and adaptable team is here to help.
            </p>
            <p>
              We specialize in assisting businesses that require expert support without the cost and commitment of hiring full-time employees. With extensive experience integrating seamlessly into existing teams, we work as an extension of your business, ensuring smooth and efficient project execution.
            </p>
          </div>
          <h2>
            Our Services
          </h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Farsi-English Translation & Interpretation</li>
            <li>Farsi & English Transcription & Subtitling</li>
            <li>Graphic Design</li>
            <li>Social Media Marketing & SEO</li>
            <li>Social Media Management</li>
            <li>Business Networking in the Iranian Market</li>
            <li>UI/UX & Web Design</li>
            <li>Article & Blog Post Writing</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            At Day Agency, we collaborate with businesses worldwide, providing hassle-free, high-quality services tailored to your needs. No matter where you are, we make working with us simple, efficient, and effective.
          </p>
          <h2>Our Tools</h2>
          <p>Scheduling and Project Management</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 list-none pl-0">
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Obsidian</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Notion</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Baserow</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">NocoDB</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Slack</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Trello</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Web Design and Web Development</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 list-none pl-0">
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">HTML</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">CSS</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">JavaScript</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">AstroJs</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">WordPress</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Translation and Transcription</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 list-none pl-0">
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">HTML</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">CSS</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">JavaScript</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">AstroJs</li>
            <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">WordPress</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Social Media Platforms</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 list-none pl-0">

          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Twitter / X</li>
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Instagram</li>
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Reddit</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Media Editing and Creation</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 list-none pl-0">
          
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Adobe Illustrator</li>
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Adobe Premiere Pro</li>
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Adobe Photoshop</li>
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Figma</li>
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Microsoft Word</li>
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Microsoft Excel</li>
          <li class="border h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl py-5 text-center">Microsoft PowerPoint</li>
        </ul>
          <hr>
          <h2>Our Team</h2>
          <Authors />
          <hr>
          <h2>Contact Us</h2>
          <div class="mx-auto flex flex-col gap-y-4 rounded-xl border p-4">
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 py-2">
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 py-2">
              <div class="flex flex-1 items-center gap-x-2 font-medium text-muted-foreground">
                Email
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <a href="mailto:daygency24@gmail.com">daygency24@gmail.com</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 py-2">
              <div class="flex flex-1 items-center gap-x-2 font-medium text-muted-foreground">
                Address
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/%DA%A9%D8%A7%D9%81%DB%8C+%D9%86%D8%AA+%D8%AF%DB%8C%E2%80%AD/@37.274082,55.157691,14z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x3f82bf0033d338fd:0x6645a3b1d5380b42!8m2!3d37.2740816!4d55.157691!16s%2Fg%2F11wy1lmky8?hl=en&entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI1MDExMC4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D">Gonbad-e-Kavoos, Golestan Province, Iran</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            
          </div>
          <h2>Daygency on the Map</h2>
          <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d12701.042569983185!2d55.1486213!3d37.265246000000005!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3f82bf0033d338fd%3A0x6645a3b1d5380b42!2z2qnYp9mB24wg2YbYqiDYr9uM!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1736915832394!5m2!1sen!2s" class="aspect-video w-full rounded-md" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
          <h2>Day Internet Café in Iran</h2>
          <p>We are based in the Golestan province of Iran, and we operate under the name of Day Internet Café. Here, we help our clients with their bureaucratic problems, offer translation services, and help them with their social media reach.</p>
          <p>You can find our Farsi website here:</p>
          <Link href="https://daynetcafe.ir" title="day internet cafe (daynetcafe)">daynetcafe.ir</Link>

        </div>
        
        

        <!-- <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Example Projects Listing</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          {projects.map((project) => <ProjectCard project={project} />)}
        </div> -->
      </div>
    </section>
  </Container>
